suncertify.server
Class URLyBirdFileHandler

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.server.URLyBirdFileHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
FileHandler
public final class URLyBirdFileHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements FileHandler

This class contains file-format dependent parsing methods for reading and writing URLyBird 1.3.2 database files. This class is thread safe.

Write a record with the specified list of Field values to the database file. This may overwrite an existing record if the existing Record is marked as "deleted". Note that this method might cause the size of the database file to increase.
